This repository contains original academic coursework (written content, maps,
and figures) produced as part of a B.A. (Hons) Geography practical
submission at Kalindi College, University of Delhi.

Permission is granted to view, reference, and cite this work for personal,
educational, and portfolio-review purposes, provided appropriate credit is
given to the author. Redistribution or reuse of substantial portions of the
written content or figures for commercial purposes is not permitted without
prior written consent from the author.

Underlying statistical data (district-level population and literacy figures)
is sourced from the Census of India, 2011, and remains subject to the
Government of India's own data usage terms.

